HEADWORD: Planishing
<hw>Plan"ish*ing</hw>, <def><pos>a. & vb. n.</pos> from
<er>Planish</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Planishing rolls</b></col> <fld>(Coining)</fld>,
<cd>rolls between which metal strips are passed while cold, to bring
them to exactly the required thickness.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

